    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras/053a2e98b2dce8c99ce5fc2d8a74d8b6.avif?t=1763331153\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras_big/053a2e98b2dce8c99ce5fc2d8a74d8b6.avif?t=1763331153 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Im Bann Der Dunklen Jagd</strong> invites you and a friend to an immersive co-op horror adventure, where you take on the role of detectives sent into a mysterious area. Your task is to gather clues and navigate through the eerie scenario. Experience the core gameplay of a level, where teamwork and careful exploration are essential to uncover the location's mystery and escape safely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras/7ecca339c82698d69ee1aa0e558804c9.webp?t=1763331153\" width=40 height=40 /></span><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperative Investigations:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is designed for two players. Work together to explore the area and find crucial objects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collecting Objects:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for clues and items scattered throughout the ominous environment. Your detective skills will be put to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras/7ecca339c82698d69ee1aa0e558804c9.webp?t=1763331153\" width=40 height=40 /></span><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Three Levels:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into three exciting levels where you work together to gather clues, solve puzzles, and successfully escape the area.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Threatening Atmosphere:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The scenario is characterized by a gloomy setting and eerie sounds that heighten the tension.</p></li></ul>",
